DTSTAMP:20260609T010621Z
UID:314981713-1780967181.926533@codecollective
DESCRIPTION:​A free\, public workshop—no technical background needed\n
 ​Most of us already know that companies\, governments\, and apps collect
  a lot of data about us. That part isn’t new.\n​What is new is what AI
  make\n\nEvent Link: https://www.meetup.com/ai-safety-awareness-group-phil
